law.text:
The Commissioner shall, to the extent that funds are available and with the advice and recommendation of the council:
Receive and disburse funds from the Kentucky Grape and Wine Council fund created in KRS 260.168;
Hire staff to carry out the duties and recommendations of the council;
Promulgate administrative regulations to carry out the duties and recommendations of the council;
Assist in the preparation of the annual report of the council; and
Monitor the activities of the council to ensure timely performance of the duties of the council under KRS 260.166.
